title: Kerbal space Program addon
description:
Kerbal Space Program:

Addon + mods



tired of limited selection for kerbal space?


============
INSTALLATION
============

To install, place the GameData folder inside your Kerbal Space Program folder. If asked to overwrite files, do so. 

Unpack everything to the root folder of the game, overwriting already existing GameData and Ships folders.

Source folder contains the source code for the included plugins and is not necessary for the mod to work.

Make sure you have KSP 0.25 or higher.


Seed Please :)
